tchen, the living room, and the bathroom. Rooms that get the most use consistently in your house. If you haven't got a lot of time, but you need an intentional, highly focused guided productivity session, then go and check it out now. I just know it's going to become a firm favorite over the summer, so make sure you bookmark it to get some clean done."}, {"shortCode": "Dap0wXLN-9F", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Dap0wXLN-9F/", "caption": "Proactive cleaning for the win \ud83d\ude4c\u2728", "timestamp": "2026-07-11T13:01:47.000Z", "videoDuration": 38.8, "videoPlayCount": 40198, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 388, "commentsCount": 7, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-hou1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/741857443_18446954164142472_5256198507200380853_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-hou1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gF1vNGRfyJFUH8dKwyxI4XZ79APnoN5yQnF_lVLAvgEbi84DK1GoZZf-Mu3LMxF4Wk&_nc_ohc=V7DuO-DSSC0Q7kNvwFFzArV&_nc_gid=22qhy0BhOQ-D5m-FnY6ShA&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQDi8OISStO3XOoH8bSocIoo3BObvf7HCFfMFhDPJyPS_A&oe=6A61A303&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQN2muscQ930aDsJfJyK8uAzJ2i52OkgIKXh7CR-TwA3OiQp3Hu7e-99uBwc3i1fVnAcb_wCtKSi5Uwyi_M4CEOU_rEuiSnxq084jAQ.mp4?_nc_cat=110&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=PHHzq6X99b0Q7kNvwEplgFI&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6OTExMTU0MjE0NzE3ODU1LCJhc3NldF9hZ2VfZGF5cyI6NywidmlfdXNlY2FzZV9pZCI6MTAwOTksImR1cmF0aW9uX3MiOjM4LCJ1cmxnZW5fc291cmNlIjoid3d3In0%3D&ccb=17-1&vs=1d0eaf1c6317e864&_nc_-pu70k6yeAxUCKAJDMywXQENmZmZmZmYYEmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MREAdf4HZeadAQA&_nc_gid=vq8nTUxq-zahIovIF-qlpw&_nc_ss=7ca8c&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQAJvwH2FTiR3LoUMVUrq5Phojgu6wMHFfw-_BdLGZeebg&oe=6A5DA947", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "the_organised_mum", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "28704532339146713"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM", "transcript": "Can I tell you the most underrated strategy for keeping your house together? It's not a deep clean. It's not a full house reset. It's just doing the small stuff before it becomes a problem. I know that sounds stupidly simple. So things like making the bed before you go downstairs in the morning, not leaving the dishes to soak, it almost feels like it shouldn't be the answer, but it actually is. The mess is always going to come back because that is just what happens when people live in houses. It's not about having the perfect aesthetic, having a home that you feel like you can truly relax in. And we do that by staying one step ahead."}, {"shortCode": "Dam0D_1N1lg", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/Dam0D_1N1lg/", "caption": "Looking for help solving the root cause and not just the symptoms? That\u2019s why I\u2019m here \ud83d\ude0d\ud83d\udc85\ud83c\udffb", "timestamp": "2026-07-10T08:58:23.000Z", "videoDuration": 35.966, "videoPlayCount": 23553, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 3, "commentsCount": 7, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/744537804_18446739643142472_1927869818625277497_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-lga3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gE3hHc2bsVcRSGA-O-1pEdnutk7UFyGxlTqTGyVdBqDHgY7Olj05Q_iHxvWthyaLeY&_nc_ohc=wSdx56hPhdYQ7kNvwG5m0QH&_nc_gid=IBlExlgR1ccKsUKF9_igBg&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQAQuac3UTjWtxuDEn-S5zoFcEVVnkrzKlYM5FR6IdK9Tg&oe=6A619D65&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-atl3-2.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m367/AQO3L_ujD9Dbd7ZI2m4zLl2sacVohB13scmZFFGuDAXiUkNVdMUiiJ-CYD4TqwnSHBsg928d4x26Taq_0y1Da9pwhKi0h6DGB041_mE.mp4?_nc_cat=101&_nc_sid=9ca052&_nc_ht=scontent-atl3-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=bQdBodR3S58Q7kNvwEUuS4M&%3D&ccb=17-1&_nc_gid=vhDD4GgFuxErNIGwDD_fQw&_nc_ss=7da8c&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_AQCDozSRu0eGBcBnF4AFeW5lc7tqzP_0jQTIAfPxbVVoNw&oe=6A61AA72", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "the_organised_mum", "song_name": "Original audio", "uses_original_audio": true, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "38037553232510663"}, "ownerUsername": "the_organised_mum", "ownerFullName": "Gemma Bray Founder of TOM", "transcript": "Look, you're probably going to really hate me for saying this, but if you love home organization content, that might be the reason why you have got so much clutter. This industry relies on you feeling overwhelmed. When you feel overwhelmed, you assume that you're failing. That makes you more susceptible to buying quick fixes. Quick fixes that don't actually fix anything at all because they're just like a sticking plaster and not dealing with the actual problem. And then you get stuck in this cycle where they don't work, so you buy more and you just keep accumulating clutter and you feel even more overwhelmed."}, {"shortCode": "DakpVovNxM8", "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DakpVovNxM8/", "caption": "And that\u2019s why we prioritise the \u2018feeling\u2019 and not the aesthetic here \ud83e\ude77\ud83d\ude4c because that is going to keep you very focused on what is worth your time, energy and money!", "timestamp": "2026-07-09T12:47:36.000Z", "videoDuration": 21.866, "videoPlayCount": 20036, "videoViewCount": null, "likesCount": 3, "commentsCount": 1, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/742876517_18446593981142472_191472840994339488_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_fr_p1080x1080_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-ord5-3.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=100&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gGneLVeTUNbqX8k9IGRKx9-gLEE3PZem6l9-vyQcZaFcu6PXq_lsuqMgee3SgGfczsACJaQJ7U1dw0cggp7OMM-&_nc_ohc=hKIlTdHW7UcQ7kNvwEbDne7&_nc_gid=70ngb86MwT4nLMCfvifUVg&edm=ADp7STQBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_AQD_GIGBwc9H6tD309-KeeqQsF8hFShMQxjuptvac2EWkw&oe=6A61A28B&_nc_sid=c6f216", "videoUrl": "https://scontent-iad3-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQMeLZLNetIVHOyI8DqZ-vnVgp8gwH1xFh_NQ